00:02:44.150 --> 00:02:46.178
with the wind on their sails,

00:02:46.178 --> 00:02:50.021
hiding their faces, exposing their bases,

00:02:50.021 --> 00:02:54.889
and sitting there in pristine glory --

00:02:54.889 --> 00:02:57.195
70 percent of India.

